            "heading": "1. How is R3 different from R1 and R2? Can I start with R3?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>R3 is designed to be gentler on gums and to support better airflow, making it a popular starting choice for many customers. Yes, you can absolutely start with R3. Our appliances do not go in any particular order.</li></ul>",
