          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. Do I need to buy R1 first, then R2, then R3?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>No. Start with the appliance that matches your needs and comfort.  </li><li>Our appliances are not meant to be used sequentially.</li></ul>",
