            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>R1 has no guarantee. Both R2 & R3 are guaranteed for one year with one free replacement. This replacement warranty is limited to one user per customer and doesn't cover repeat purchases of the same appliance.</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_zPxeBW": {
