            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>Contact support at <a href=\"mailto:cs@getreviv.com\" target=\"_blank\">cs@getreviv.com</a> with your goals (comfort, airflow, grinding, budget) and we’ll recommend the best option.</li></ul>",
